 <em style="strong">ISOs can be downloaded from our <link type="seealso" href="https://github.com/ublue-os/bazzite/releases">releases page</link>, and a helpful install guide can be found <link type="seealso" href="https://universal-blue.discourse.group/docs?topic=30">here</link>.</em></p>

 <p>Rebase from an existing upstream Fedora Atomic to this image:</p>
 <p><code>bash
